modelVersions.name: Nilou
modelVersions.description:
关键词：((nilou_realistic)), ((beautiful face)), (blue eyes), (navel), (red long hair, twin tails, skirt,crop top, long sleeves, o-ring legwear, nilou's sandals),

权重的话，根据自己的情况来，慢慢往上摸，摸到比较像的时候就不用升权重了，我这边建议0.6到0.75（给萌新们科普一下，LORA的权重在保证还原度的同时能低则低，可以避免很多问题）

*** 注：因为训练集里的coser们的腿部动作比较浮夸，导致AI学习效果不佳，故采用了正则化对腿部动作予以纠正，所以最好在prompt里加入standing naturally with no pose, 并给予一个较高权重（1.3到1.5），可有效缓解腿部错误

Instruction of Nilou

Trigger words：((nilou_realistic)), ((beautiful face)), (blue eyes), (navel), (red long hair, twin tails, skirt,crop top, long sleeves, o-ring legwear, nilou's sandals),

Lora's weight: 0.6~0.75

*** I used regularization to correct the leg postures because the leg postures of the cosplayers in the training set is rather exaggerated. so you'd better put "standing naturally with no pose" into prompt, and give a high weight (1.3 ~ 1.5) to it, which can effectively alleviate the leg problems
